---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ContentHero from '../../components/ContentHero.astro';
import ContentBlock from '../../components/ContentBlock.astro';
import TakeAction from '../../components/TakeAction.astro';
---

<Layout title="Landowners">
	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<ContentHero
		imgAlt="Group of people on a hillside."
		imgSrc="/hero-landowners.jpg"
		title="Landowners"
	>
		<p>
			Take your land from idle to ideal with help from Protect Earth. We'll work with you to enhance
			the ecosystem health of your land.
		</p>
		<p>
			We work with landowners, land managers and farmers to increase tree cover, improve
			biodiversity, and restore ecosystems – without breaking the bank or burying you in paperwork.
		</p>
	</ContentHero>

	<!-- Reforesting or Rewilding Section -->
	<ContentBlock
		imgSrc="/landowners-rewilding.jpg"
		imgAlt="Open grassy field with scattered patches."
		title="Reforesting or Rewilding Your Land"
	>
		<p>
			Enhancing your land for nature and wildlife has never been easier. We can plant shelterbelts
			and field trees to provide shade and protection for livestock. In unused areas, we can
			establish thriving woodlands or vibrant wildflower meadows that act as productive carbon
			stores. For those with existing woodlands, we offer expert management to restore or maintain
			healthy, biodiverse ecosystems.
		</p>
	</ContentBlock>

	<!-- Agroforestry Section -->
	<ContentBlock
		imgAlt="Muddy field with newly installed fencing."
		imgSrc="/landowners-agroforestry.jpg"
		title="Agroforestry"
		isReversed
	>
		<p>
			If navigating government funding feels like an uphill battle, Protect Earth can help. We'll
			guide you in your rewilding, agroforestry (i.e. shelterbelts, silvopasture), or other
			nature-focused efforts. If grants are available, we'll help you apply (and you keep the
			funding). If not, we can use charitable donations to cover the costs. Either way, we'll help
			you make meaningful improvements at little to no expense.
		</p>
	</ContentBlock>

	<!-- Lease or Donate Land Section -->
	<ContentBlock
		imgSrc="/landowners-rewilding.jpg"
		imgAlt="Open grassy field with scattered patches."
		title="Lease or Donate Land"
	>
		<p>
			Want to see your land transformed but don't have the time or resources? Lease or donate it to
			Protect Earth.
		</p>
		<p>
			We'll conduct surveys, carry out planting, and ensure the long-term care and protection of the
			space. Donating or leasing land is a straightforward, impactful way to contribute to nature
			restoration. <a href="/contact">Get in touch</a> to discuss how we can work together.
		</p>
	</ContentBlock>

	<!-- Application Form Section -->
	<section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
		<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
			<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
				Apply for Biodiversity Assistance & Funding
			</h2>
			<p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8">
				Fill out the application form below to tell us more about your land and your goals.
			</p>
			<a
				href="https://noteforms.com/forms/form-landowner-applications-kifqm4"
				target="_blank"
				rel="noopener noreferrer"
				class="inline-block bg-green-700 hover:bg-green-800 text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded transition text-lg"
			>
				Application Form →
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<TakeAction />
</Layout>
